{
  "texts": [
    "To test the prevalence of errors made by GPT, students were asked every week if the tutor had made some errors in their chats.",
    "Of 160 responses, only 16 indicated a problem.",
    "Going over all the marked exercises, we concluded that there were no more than 14 utterances that could be considered problematic.",
    "We also randomly went over 10% of the conversations and did not find any additional issues.",
    "Given that the total number of utterances is around 4000, the error rate is less than 0.5% which is well within acceptable thresholds."
  ]
}